/*
    File: fn_fastSum.sqf
    Author:
    Date: 2025-09-19
    Last Update: 2025-09-19
    Public: No

    Description:
        Quickly sums an array using vectorDotProduct.

        Only works on less than 1000 items right now (due to the size of the ONES array).
        Extend the ONES array if you need more values - the 1000 item limit is arbitrary.

    Parameter(s):
        _values - Values to sum [ARRAY]

    Returns:
        Sum of all array values [NUMBER]

    Example(s):
        [[2,2,2]] call vgm_g_fastSum;
 */

